cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is about training deep video models efficiently, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of multigrid methods is a numerical optimization technique, which could also place this paper in the mathematical modeling (cs.MM) category. Additionally, the paper proposes a general and robust grid schedule, which involves scheduling and optimization, and could be relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
